name: Aqueduct Sunset
description: Beautiful, unique and atmospheric sunset background surrounding your truck in the main menu of American Truck Simulator. Enjoy!

name: Polar Star
description: A little cabin decoration to take the spirit of Christmas along with you on the road.

name: Polar Plush Bear
description: It's so fluffy! Take this little fellow with you on your travels across the American roads!

name: Magic Time
description: Celebrate Christmas time with this beautiful background theme! There is a gift for everyone under this tree!

name: Grizzly Bear
description: Let this mighty beast accompany you on your travels and keep you safe from harm!

name: Snowman Trucker
description: Everyone wants to be a trucker! Even snowmen! Just think twice before you'll turn on the heating in your cabin!

name: Crystal Dream
description: Dreams can be beautiful but fragile as a crystal... Use this rare paint job and keep your deliveries safe while you pursue your dreams.

name: On top of the world
description: Your private parking space at the gates of the North Pole. Parking is allowed only to a chosen few for their mighty trucks here!

name: Plush Excavator
description: A cute little friend of the massive iron beasts used during the real landslide cleanup. However, you can take this one with you on your journeys!

name: Plush Excavator Rare
description: A rare variant of the cute plush excavator. A little friend of the massive iron beasts used during the real landslide cleanup. However, you can take this one with you on your journeys!

name: Juggernaut
description: A tough-looking custom paint job made to fit the occasion and bring back memories of the difficult deliveries performed during Operation Big Sur.

name: Operation Big Sur
description: A special paint job to commemorate the unique Operation Big Sur. Let's celebrate the day when the community united and restored Californian Highway 1. Together we made it!

name: Edge Tracer (Truck)
description: Jump in your cab and take your drive the extra mile with this unique Edge Tracer paint job for your truck.

name: Edge Tracer (Trailer)
description: Jump in your cab and take your drive the extra mile with this unique Edge Tracer paint job for your trailer.

name: Xmas Tree
description: A cute little golden tree planted in the tire. Subtle but cool hanging interior decoration. An award for those who made an extra effort completing personal contribution of World of Trucks' Christmas Event 2018 in both American Truck Simulator and Euro Truck Simulator 2.

name: Timber Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 250,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang this excellent piece of wooden art in your cabin!

name: Craftsman Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 500,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang this piece of precise leather-work in your cabin!

name: Silver Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 750,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang it as a fine piece of an exclusive silver jewellery!

name: Golden Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 1,000,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang it as a piece of fine 999 gold jewellery!

name: Magical Spiral
description: You didn't believe in fairy tales until you found the magical snowflake in your cabin as a reward for your hauling duty. No one knows where it comes from.

name: First Class
description: Haul hard, relax like a millionaire. And that goes for your truck as well. Park it in the First Class hangar and give it the luxury care it deserves.

name: Platinum Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 1,250,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang it as a fine piece of a rare metal jewellery!

name: Festive Tree
description: A memory relic of taking part in reaching 1,500,000 deliveries in the World of Trucks Christmas event in 2018. Hang it and make your cabin festive like it's Christmas time!

name: Boxing Gloves
description: What better way to symbolise the fight against breast cancer than a pair of pink ribbon emblazoned Boxing Gloves! Add them to your cabin to show your support for the cause.

name: Winning Dice
description: We all appreciate winning dice from time to time, and these also show pink ribbons however they roll! Add them to your cabin to show your support in the fight against breast cancer.

name: Honey Bee
description: The honey bee, Apis mellifera, the official state insect of Utah and a great mascot to have hanging in your truck cabin as you drive through Utah's scenic routes.

name: Christmas Sock
description: What goodies can be found in this attractive wool knit Christmas Sock. Add it to your cabin to celebrate the season of giving!

name: Under Wraps
description: What secret delivery will you be making in this beautiful Christmas themed paint job during this season of giving.

name: Crystal Chill
description: Every snowflake crystal in the world is unique, and so is this amazing paint job. Paint your truck with it to chill out while driving.

name: Spot the Holly
description: Straight out of a stylish, early 20th century parlour, this paint job offers hidden holly branches in a charming vintage pattern. Visit the spirit of Christmas past with it.

name: Autumn Star
description: A shiny ornamental reward for reaching 200 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hang it within your cabin in preparation for the holiday season.

name: Twinkle Star
description: An eye catching ornamental reward for reaching 400 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hang it in your cabin with pride of the community's achievement.

name: Frosty Star
description: A very cool ornamental reward for reaching 600 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hang it up in your cabin, you'll be cool and frosty while driving.

name: Winter Star
description: A dazzling ornamental reward for reaching 800 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Enjoy its many pretty facets as it hangs in your cabin.

name: Christmas Star
description: A beautiful ornamental reward for reaching 1000 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hang it in your cabin as a tribute to the spirit of Christmas giving!

name: Wishing Star
description: A very special ornamental reward for reaching 1200 stars in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. What will you wish for with this hanging in your cabin?

name: Diamond Star
description: An impressive ornamental reward for helping the community by delivering more than the personal goal limit, in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hang it in your cabin for bling that only a diamond star can bring!

name: Grand Star
description: A magnificent ornamental reward for helping the community by delivering no less than twice the personal goal limit, in the Christmas Grand Giving event 2019. Hanging in your cabin, it will symbolise an unmatched personal contribution towards the community goal!

name: Home Trucker Insignia
description: This beautifully embossed, shiny Home Trucker Insignia represents our thanks and your achievement in keeping the world a safer place during our unprecedented Truck At Home event. Hang it in your cabin with pride!

name: Leopard Tracks
description: Adorn your truck with a statement of strength and beauty from Idaho, with this Appaloosa themed paint job.

name: Bareback Blanket
description: Adorn your truck with a statement of strength and beauty from Idaho, with this Appaloosa themed paint job.

name: Peregrine Gem
description: This silver Peregrine Falcon, the official state raptor of Idaho, carries with it a Star Garnet symbolising two rare and natural treasures found in Idaho. Hang it in your cabin as a memento of your visit to this beautiful state.

name: Hard Truck Heat
description: This limited edition paint job celebrates 18 years since 2002, when SCS Software created their first truck simulation game Hard Truck: 18 Wheels of Steel. Show it off while cruising Colorado to enjoy a trip down memory lane.

name: Big Rocky
description: The mighty Rocky Mountain Bighorn, Ovis canadensis, the official state animal of Colorado. With an impressive paint job like this the message is clear - coming through!

name: Rocky Rodeo Gem
description: This silver and gold shield encapsulates three famous icons, unique to Colorado. The magnificent Rocky Mountains, the Western Stock Show and Rodeo, and the beautiful state gemstone Aquamarine. Hang it in your cabin as your souvenir for taking part in the Cruising Colorado event!

name: Winter Blast
description: With such a smashing paint job as this, you're sure to have a cool blast this Christmas! Paint your truck with it this season of giving.

name: Winter Bauble
description: A charming snowy tribute for reaching the first community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Hang it in your cabin for that special memory.

name: Festive Mug
description: A thirst busting mug, with a friendly Merry Christmas wish, for reaching the second community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Perfect for a nice hot chocolate on those long cold hauls.

name: Wise Heart Pillow
description: A great place to rest your weary head, with the promise of sweet dreams, for reaching the third community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Pack it for your rest stops.

name: Holly Field Blanket
description: A snugly warm blanket of festive red and green holly, for reaching the fourth community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Great for a quick nap between jobs.

name: Winter Blast Gift
description: A gift box that matches the Gifts cargo you so wisely delivered, for reaching the fifth community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Hang it in your cabin to match your Winter Blast paint job!

name: Wise Owl Offering
description: The ultimate trophy for the wisest of givers, and cutest of owls, that celebrates you reaching the the sixth and final community tier in the Christmas Wise Giving event of 2020. Hang it in your cabin with pride!

name: Hope Trucker Insignia
description: This smartly embossed Hope Trucker Insignia is our way of saying thanks and recognition for your achievement in delivering COVID-19 Vaccines, and hope, in World of Trucks, during the Hauling Hope event. Hang it in your cabin with great pride!

name: Best Community Ever (Truck)
description: As our reward for the Best Community Ever, we offer you a very special, one-of-a-kind, SCS community tribute paint job. Paint your truck with it as a #BestCommunityEver member!

name: Best Community Ever (Trailer)
description: As our reward for the Best Community Ever, we offer you a very special, one-of-a-kind, SCS community tribute paint job. Paint your trailer with it as a #BestCommunityEver member!

name: Wooden Bowl of Chips
description: Enjoy this delicious wooden bowl of potato chips, as our thank you, for delivering Idahoâ€™s famous potatoes during the Idaho Spuds event. Place it in your cab as your tasty treat.

name: Giant Salamander Sticker
description: This cool Giant Salamander sticker is the perfect tribute gift for achieving your personal goal during the Idaho Spuds event, since itâ€™s the Stateâ€™s national amphibian! Add it to your sleeper cab.

name: Idaho Nights Air Freshener
description: Hang this peaceful and soothing air freshener in your cab to get you through the long hauls. Let it remind you of Idaho's 1st year anniversary since release, and of your celebratory potato deliveries.

name: Idaho Spuds Sticker
description: This fun little potato trophy sticker will stand proud in your sleeper cab, as a tribute to you for taking part in and achieving the Idaho Spuds event community goal.

name: Thrustmaster T248 Mini Wheel
description: Enjoy this hanging mini wheel as a memento of being part of our joint celebration in the launch of the latest Thrustmaster T248.

name: Bison Brawler
description: The American bison, the official state mammal of Wyoming, was significant for the Native tribes of the American Plains not just as food, shelter and clothing, but it also served as a powerful spiritual symbol. Praise the power of the bison with this beautiful paint job.

name: Jade Bison
description: The American Bison was important for the Native tribes of the Great Plains as it provided a way of life and served as a powerful spiritual symbol. Made from Wyoming's state gem stone, display this prestigious Jade Bison ornament as a memento of your journey during the Cruising Wyoming event.

name: Triceratops Plush
description: The Triceratops, that lived in Wyoming over 65 million years ago, is the official state dinosaur of today. As a herbivore, its three horns, though fearsome-looking, were for defense only. Place this cute Triceratops Plush next to you as a companion during your long journeys.

name: Thrustmaster T248 Mini Pedals
description: These T248 mini pedals are a perfect match for our hanging T248 mini wheel which is also available after logging in to WorldofTrucks.com with your browser. A great way to celebrate the launch of the latest Thrustmaster T248 steering wheel during our Steering Wheel Roll-Out event!

name: Decorative Cab Lights
description: What a brilliantly lit way to decorate your favourite cab this season of giving! Add it to your truck for a perfect lighting match with the Christmas event trailers this year.

name: The Nutcracker's Guard
description: May this guardian of toys watch over you and your collection of cabin rewards. What a perfect start for reaching the first tier in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021.

name: Push N Go Race Car
description: This nostalgic racer sits shiny and proud, a fine example of beautiful workmanship. Your reward for reaching the second tier in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021. Let it inspire your journeys.

name: Walnut Rocking Horse
description: The gentle rocking of this wonderfully crafted horse provides a calming and cheerful vibe for any long haul. Your reward for reaching the third tier in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021.

name: Willy Wind Up Mouse
description: What a cute little fella to keep you company in your cabin. No trouble nor fuss, with an old clockwork soul that charms. Enjoy your fourth tier reward in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021.

name: Old Oak Steam Train
description: Behold, your fifth tier reward in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021. The classic steam engine, offering ageless appeal, fine construction, and rich wood grains that echo the stories and laughter of Christmas past.

name: Yesteryear Teddy Bear
description: Here is a resilient teddy of times gone by, one who still implores you for cuddles and smiles, and rewards you with the love that was used to make this lovely toy. Your reward for reaching the sixth tier in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021.

name: Clicky the Robot
description: This enchanting robot still begs a fascination as a vision of the future that was created in the past. It is a toy that celebrates the highest level of vintage creativity and aspiration, and also is your seventh and final tier reward in the Christmas Toys of Yesteryear event of 2021. Place it in your cabin and be inspired!

name: Montana Grizzly
description: Cherish the strength and beauty of the majestic grizzly bear. The official state animal is unique to Montana since its conserving the largest population of the endangered species for more than a century. Bear up and grace your truck with this beautiful paint job.

name: Sapphire Meadowlark
description: Found in open grasslands in Montana, the protected Western Meadowlark is known for its cheerful singing. Remember your journey during the Cruising Montana event and have this prestigious Sapphire Meadowlark ornament, made from Montana's state gem stone, displayed in your cabin.

name: Mountain Goat Plush
description: The white Mountain Goat can be found thriving in the wild ranges of the Rocky Mountains. So, as a friendly memento of your trip to Kalispell in Montana, we offer you this worthy Mountain Goat Plush as your companion on your journeys.

name: Swinging Bat
description: This creepy, yet cute, swinging bat keeps its bright beady eyes on you as it swings back and forth, while perched upside-down on an enchanted tree. The perfect companion for your spooky travels during the Happy Hauloween event!

name: Pumpkin Head
description: Who doesnâ€™t love a dangling pumpkin head with a wicked grin to keep you company during a dark stormy night of hauling. Its glowing face will surely make you smile and remember your contribution to achieving the community goal for our Happy Hauloween event of 2022!

name: Horned Lizard
description: Give your truck this fierce-looking Horned Lizard paint job. This friendly creature is often found sunbathing in the rocky areas of Texas, where it is celebrated as the state reptile. What a great way to remember your journeys with this wonderful paint job.

name: Lone Star Longhorn
description: The skull of the Texas Longhorn with the Lone Star stateâ€™s blue topaz gemstone, is a powerful symbol for strength, agility and resilience. Hang this finely crafted Lone Star Longhorn ornament in your cabin and feel its power during your rides through the second biggest state of America.

name: Armadillo Plush
description: Texans and armadillos have more in common than you might think. Besides being the stateâ€™s official small mammal, the armadillo shares a respect for the land where it lives, an ability to adapt and overcome challenges, and like so many Texans, a fierce undying love for freedom. Let this cute Texan Armadillo Plush ride along as your journey through the second biggest state of America.

name: Lines of Reflection (Truck)
description: This is such a cool and calm paint job, with the beginning of lines to evoke love, peace, hope and care. All the shared memories from this season of Christmas Reflections.

name: Love Pillow
description: There is no mistaking the loving message from such a generous and festive pillow as this. Perfect to snuggle into this season of giving.

name: Peace Dove
description: This hanging white peace dove is a thing of beauty, it's also known to bring some calm during stressful drives. Hang it in your cabin this season of thoughtful giving.

name: Candle of Hope
description: What better way to symbolize hope and light the spirits of you and those around you this Christmas, than with this lovely festive candle.

name: Care Blanket
description: The warmth and protection from this care infused blanket is undenyable. Perfect for a quick snooze or leg warmer to restore your energy while hauling your Christmas Gifts this season.

name: Lines of Reflection (Trailer)
description: A beautiful and calm paint job, that completes the lines of reflection on love, peace, hope and care. All the shared memories from this season of Christmas Reflections.

name: Trucker Cupid
description: Hang this winged messenger of love in your truck and let the Trucker Cupid lead you with his bow and arrow to find love and passion during romantic rides towards the sunset.

name: Box of Chocolate
description: Treat yourself with a delicious Box of Chocolate and share with your loved ones as a sign of love and care for them.

name: Wild Stampede
description: Embrace the strength of the mighty bison, Oklahoma's official state animal, preserved and protected by the Sooner State. Let this Wild Stampede paint job guide you through the mist and clear a path with untamed power.

name: Black Swallowtail
description: Oklahomaâ€™s beautiful black swallowtail is not only the official state butterfly but is also important for supporting the stateâ€™s plant life and ecology. Hang this golden Black Swallowtail in your cabin and let it shine the way ahead on your journeys.

name: Honey Bee Plush
description: The honey bee, an extraordinary pollinator for over 30 million years and vital to the Oklahoma's agriculture is the official state insect. Cherish this tiny wonder of nature by inviting the cute Honey Bee Plush to ride along with you during long journeys.

name: Spooky Spider
description: Youâ€™ll have a ball with this spooky spider hanging in your cab, and what a great companion for your journeys throughout Halloween. The dark design on its fluffy purple body serves to remind you of your contribution to achieving the community goal for our Happy Hauloween event of 2023!

name: Count Catula Plush
description: This incredibly cute black cat sits on your seat, master of all that it sees, watching you intently while you drive. Who knows what it is thinking, perhaps it is simply waiting for a cuddle! What a purrfect companion for your spooky deliveries during the Happy Hauloween event!

name: Sunflower Sunset
description: Embrace beautiful reflections of Kansas by combining two iconic state symbols: the sunflower, symbolism of faith, happiness and optimism with the Western Meadowlark. Adorn your truck with this Sunflower Sunset paint job and embark on your journey toward the setting sun in style.

name: Amber Sunflower
description: Kansans share a profound bond with the sunflower, which serves as their state flower, intricately woven into their past, present, and future. Combined with the state's national gemstone, Jelinite Amber â€“ a rare fossilized tree resin â€“ this captivating golden Amber Sunflower will lead the way as you embark on a journey through the incredible landscapes of the Sunflower State.

name: Tiger Salamander
description: The barred tiger salamander, state amphibian of Kansas, though known to be the world's largest land-dwelling salamander, is not easily found in the wild, as they spend their adult life hidden from daylight. Count yourself lucky to have such a friendly companion as this Tiger Salamander Plush, with a perpetual grin, to invite for the ride on your journeys.

name: Winterland
description: This cheerfully chilly, and very Christmassy paint job will always remind you of the fun and magic had during your travels to Winterland this season of giving!

name: Christmas Sweater
description: There's nothing like a snugly Christmas Sweater to keep you cosy and warm on those chilly nights, especially at the Snowy Peaks Mountain Resort. Its cheerful and cheeky design is perfect!

name: Festive Chocolates
description: What a decadently delicious dish to keep by your side as you work in earnest delivering Christmas cheer to and from Marigold's Chocolate Factory. Go on, have another one, you deserve it!

name: Golden North Star
description: Let this beautiful golden north star shine and lead the way through Christmas Winterland, and to the Northstar Post Office! Hang it in your cabin this season of giving.

name: Rudolph's Sleigh
description: Who knows what goodies are stored in Rudolph's sleigh this Christmas, but you sure helped fill it this season of giving, thank you! Keep this as your memento to Winterland and Rudolph's Crafts workshop!

name: Winterland Christmas Tree
description: What better defines the season of giving than a wondrous and magical Christmas tree? We give this to you in honour of your help with delivering supplies and gift packs to and from the Christmas Market Town Square. Thank you!

name: Winged Heart
description: Cruise the open roads with a touch of romance and take along the Winged Heart pillow, turning your cab into a haven of comfort and cosiness on your journey over the highways of love.

name: Trucker's Rose
description: Spice up your truck with a touch of romance and let this Trucker's Rose steal the spotlight in your cab as you roll off on a new journey to capture hearts!

name: Mighty Mammoth
description: Grace your truck with the powerful image of the Columbian Mammoth. This ancient giant serves as a timeless symbol of courage and endurance, perfectly suited to accompany you on your long journeys.

name: Box Turtle
description: Hang this beautifully ornate Box Turtle pendant, inspired by Nebraska's state reptile and using the stateâ€™s blue agate gem stone, as your prestigious memento for your trip across the Cornhusker State.

name: Mammoth Archie
description: 'Archie' is known as the biggest Columbian mammoth of Nebraska and serves a symbol of resilience and unity. Invite this cute version of the legendary giant into your truck as your companion when travelling through the diverse landscapes of Nebraska.

name: White-tailed Watch
description: Adorn your ride with this majestic image of the white-tailed deer. Ever watchful and alert, this stunning paint job depicts the Arkansas' state animal perfectly for your journey through the country side .

name: Diamond Apple Blossom
description: This rose gold pendent depicts the beautiful Arkansas apple blossom, selected as the state flower due to the stateâ€™s impressive history of apple production. It holds a central diamond, representing the state gem, which shines brightly reminding you of your wonderful journeys through the incredible Natural State.

name: White-tailed Deer
description: The white-tailed deer, state mammal of Arkansas, is not only beautiful to look at but also a great swimmer, can jump up to eight feet high and has a unique white tail which can warn other deer of danger. Enjoy the company of this cute little White-Tailed Deer fawn in your cab, during your journeys through Arkansas, the Natural State.

name: Booing Ghost
description: This ghostly guest in your cab may surprise you, now and then, with a boo! Well, itâ€™s what ghosts do best right? Consider it our friendly way of saying congratulations for achieving your personal goal of deliveries during the Happy Hauloween event of 2024!

name: Grumpy Ghost
description: If you fancy a floating apparition in your cab as company, during your spooky Halloween deliveries, then this hanging Grumpy Ghost is the perfect companion for you! Our thanks for your contribution to achieving the community goal for our Happy Hauloween event of 2024!

name: Decorative Cab Lights Assortment
description: What a dazzling way to brighten up your truck this season of giving! This assortment of six vibrant sets â€“ Blue, Green, Red, Yellow, Gold, and a beautiful Xmas mix â€“  provide a perfect lighting match for your holiday rig with the Return to Winterland event trailers this Christmas.

name: Christmas Hat and Mittens
description: This cosy set of Christmas Woolly Hat and Mittens is sure to keep you warm and toasty on those frosty winter days, especially at the Snowy Peaks Mountain Resort. Their festive design is a perfect way to spread some holiday cheer!

name: Marigold's Chocolates
description: Thereâ€™s nothing like a festive box of Marigold's Chocolates to treat your sweet tooth this holiday season. Go ahead and indulge â€“ youâ€™ve earned every bite of this delicious, handcrafted assortment!

name: Festive Gingerbread Stamps
description: These mouthwatering gingerbread biscuits embody the Christmas spirit of the Northstar Post Office, their colourful design representing festive postage stamps from Winterland. Enjoy them with a nice hot cuppa during a delivery break this season of giving.

name: White Deer
description: This lovingly sculpted white deer is your special reward from Rudolphâ€™s Crafts workshop. Consider it our thank you for all your hard work with the Christmas deliveries this year. May it bring you peace and harmony on your winter journeys.

name: Christmas Bells
description: May these beautifully fashioned Christmas bells ring cheerfully for you and all you hold dear. Your reward, with gratitude, from the Christmas Market Town Square â€“ our thanks for delivering supplies and gift packs this year.

name: Neon Heart
description: Brighten your dashboard with the Neon Heart sign, a glowing symbol of love that transforms every drive into a heartfelt experience. Let its gentle radiance create a cozy, romantic atmosphere wherever the road takes you.

name: Cupid's Dice
description: Hang Cupid's Dice in your vehicle and let love and luck roll with every turn. These playful charms bring a touch of romance to your journey, making each ride an unforgettable adventure.

name: Beast of Burden
description: Saddle up for the journey with the Beast of Burden paint job! Inspired by the rugged spirit of the Show-Me State, this design brings bold colors and grit to your rig, making every haul an adventure.

name: Striking Mule
description: Bring some rustic charm to your cab with this hand carved wooden Striking Mule. A symbol of strength and determination, itâ€™s the perfect companion for life on the road.

name: Show-Me Pillow
description: Add comfort and state pride to your cabin with the Show-Me Pillow! Featuring the iconic Show-Me tartan, a vibrant bluebird, and delicate hawthorn blossoms, it's a cozy nod to Missouri heritage.

name: Tom Hopper
description: Meet Tom Hopper, the American bullfrog ready to ride shotgun! Sporting a charming straw hat, this plush companion brings a touch of whimsy southern charm to your passenger seat.

name: Golden Flight
description: Ride out with this stunning paint job, featuring a Goldfinch soaring through a swirl of oak leaves. Capture the spirit of the state's natural beauty and add a touch of Iowa's wildlife to your truck!

name: Porcelain Wild Rose
description: Decorate your truck interior with this elegant pendant featuring the iconic Iowa Wild Rose. A symbol of the state's beauty and resilience, it also adds a touch of nature-inspired charm to your ride.

name: Happy Hog
description: Enjoy a bit of Iowa's rural charm with the Happy Hog. This soft and cuddly plush captures the spirit of Iowa's agricultural heritage and makes a perfect travel buddy for your journeys.

name: Witch's Compass
description: Behold! The witches have recognised your valiant deeds and rewarded you with this Witch's Compass. With it, youâ€™ll never lose your way in these haunted lands. Let it stand as a symbol of your spooky adventures and the role you played in our Witches of Brackenreach event!

name: Black Cat
description: What better symbol for a witchâ€™s power than a black cat? Youâ€™ve earned this emblem as a mark of your contribution to the community goal. Let it serve as a reminder in your cab that your efforts helped make our Witches of Brackenreach event a spellbinding success!

name: Spooky Horn
description: The witches are in your favour and in your debt! Your fearless exploration has earned you a Spooky Horn, their gift to you. Let its sound echo across the land, a proud signal that you braved the spooky adventures of our Witches of Brackenreach event!

name: Southern Wings
description: Adorn your truck with this stunning tribute to the Pelican State! Louisianaâ€™s iconic pelicans are a common sight along the coast â€” gliding low over the waves, diving for fish, and nesting in the quiet marshes. Now itâ€™s your turn to spread your wings and hit the road in true Bayou style!

name: Golden South
description: Carry a piece of Louisiana wherever the road leads. This pendant shines with the proud spirit of the Pelican State â€” a timeless emblem for every mile through moss-draped bayous and highways steeped in Southern charm.

name: Boudreaux the Bear
description: Black bears are quiet guardians of the wild â€” resilient, curious, and always on the move. Often spotted in Louisianaâ€™s river deltas, they embody the spirit of the untamed. Let Boudreaux be your mighty companion, a symbol of respect and love for nature.
